{"id": "art-125", "label": "Art. 125", "title": "Art. 125", "slug": "art-125", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:\nblack'>Art. 125 </span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_680338231\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2300\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_680338231\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1)<span class=SpellE>Ac&#355;ionarii</span> pot participa <span\nclass=SpellE>&#351;i</span> vota în adunarea general&#259; prin reprezentare,\nîn baza unei împuterniciri acordate pentru respectiva adunare general&#259;.</span><br\nstyle='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_312413003\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2299\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_312413003\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2)<span class=SpellE>Ac&#355;ionarii</span> care nu au\ncapacitate de <span class=SpellE>exerci&#355;iu</span>, precum <span\nclass=SpellE>&#351;i</span> persoanele juridice pot fi <span class=SpellE>reprezenta&#355;i</span>/reprezentate\nprin <span class=SpellE>reprezentan&#355;ii</span> lor legali care, la rândul\nlor, pot da altor persoane împuternicire pentru respectiva adunare\ngeneral&#259;.</span><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_795974941\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2298\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_795974941\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(3)Procurile vor fi depuse în original cu 48 de ore înainte\nde adunare sau în termenul prev&#259;zut de actul constitutiv, sub <span\nclass=SpellE>sanc&#355;iunea</span> pierderii <span class=SpellE>exerci&#355;iului</span>\ndreptului de vot în acea adunare. Procurile vor fi <span class=SpellE>re&#355;inute</span>\nde societate, f&#259;cându-se <span class=SpellE>men&#355;iune</span> despre\naceasta în procesul-verbal.</span><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='color:black'>(4)[textul din Art. 125, alin. (4)\ndin titlul III, capitolul IV, <span class=SpellE>sectiunea</span> II a fost\nabrogat la 01-dec-2006 de </span><span style='color:#1B1B1B'>Art. I, punctul\n69. din <i style='mso-bidi-font-style:normal'>Legea</i> 441/2006</span><span\nstyle='color:black'>]</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1961379247\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2297\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1961379247\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(5)Membrii consiliului de <span class=SpellE>administra&#355;ie</span>,\ndirectorii, respectiv membrii directoratului <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>\nai consiliului de supraveghere, ori <span class=SpellE>func&#355;ionarii</span>\n<span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span> nu îi pot reprezenta pe <span\nclass=SpellE>ac&#355;ionari</span>, sub <span class=SpellE>sanc&#355;iunea</span>\n<span class=SpellE>nulit&#259;&#355;ii</span> hot&#259;rârii, dac&#259;,\nf&#259;r&#259; votul acestora, nu s-ar fi <span class=SpellE>ob&#355;inut</span>\nmajoritatea cerut&#259;.</span><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>"}